    "At the same time, there needs to be more effective countermeasures for the partial overlapping point cloud registration.",
    "With the application of deep learning in the field of point cloud registration, a number of methods have emerged to solve the problem of low overlap point cloud registration.",
    "As shown in Figure 2, it can be seen that since 2016, the relevant literatures about deep learning point cloud registration have shown a blowout growth and are still increasing.",
